      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1841 - Hisham ibn al-Hakam narrated from Abu Abdullah (Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as)), who said:\n\"Whoever is not forgiven during the Month of Ramadan will not be forgiven until the following year, except if they witness the Day of Arafah.\""
